{"arkId":"cl010097017","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010097017","modified ":"2026-03-11","title":"Couronne aux cam\u00e9es, dite \u0022couronne de Charlemagne\u0022","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Couronne aux cam\u00e9es, dite \u0022couronne de Charlemagne\u0022"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Premier Empire (1804-1814) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque contemporaine)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1804","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 504 - Sceptre de Charles V, Vitrine 2","room":"Salle 504, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1804,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"D\u00e9but du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Biennais, Martin-Guillaume","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1764","place":"Coch\u00e8re (La)","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1843","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"source documentaire ou archivistique","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q1694164"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"MS 91","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"couronne","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Couronne ferm\u00e9e dont les huit branches se rejoignent sous une boule somm\u00e9e d\u0027une croix ; le bord sup\u00e9rieur du bandeau dessine alternativement une palmette et une boule. Le bandeau et les branches sont orn\u00e9s de quarante cam\u00e9es, provenant des tr\u00e9sors de Bourges, d\u0027Arpajon et de Saint-Denis, pr\u00e9lev\u00e9s dans le fonds du mus\u00e9e par Vivant Denon. Coiffe en velours violet brod\u00e9 fournie par Jacques-Evrard Bapst pour le sacre de Charles X.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; Couronne de \/ Charlemagne (sur un \u00e9cu au-dessus de l\u0027\u00e9crin)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"25","displayDimension":"25 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"18,5","displayDimension":"18,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"26","displayDimension":"26 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"28,4","displayDimension":"28,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"23,8","displayDimension":"23,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : vermeil = argent dor\u00e9\r\nTechnique : intaille (techniques pierre\/ciment\/pl\u00e2tre\/cire-\u003Egrav\u00e9)\r\nTechnique : taille en cam\u00e9e (techniques pierre\/ciment\/pl\u00e2tre\/cire-\u003Etaill\u00e9 = taille)\r\nTechnique : velours (techniques textile-\u003Etissu uni)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[{"value":"Tr\u00e9sor, Le tr\u00e9sor de Saint-Denis, Saint-Denis"},{"value":"Sacre, Les Regalia - Les instruments du sacre des rois de France - Les \u0022Honneurs de Charlemagne\u0022, France"}],"objectHistory":"Ex\u00e9cut\u00e9e pour figurer parmi les\u0022 Honneurs de Charlemagne\u0022 au sacre de Napol\u00e9on Ier, la couronne fut orn\u00e9e de cam\u00e9es, provenant pour la plupart d\u0027un reliquaire offert \u00e0 Saint-Denis, en 1401, par Jean, duc de Berry. La couronne fut expos\u00e9e de 1804 \u00e0 1816 \u00e0 Notre-Dame de Paris ; d\u00e9pos\u00e9e au Garde-Meuble, restaur\u00e9e par Bapst pour le sacr